    "description": [
      "A faint sound like chiming crystals comes in tantalizing snatches on the shrill wind blowing off of the Issenflow to the south.  Spruce, pine, and hoarbeam trees form an unusually thick canopy overhead, heavy enough to block view of the sky, though not quite enough to keep the driving snow from the earth.  The trail is littered with needles in every shade from emerald green to blanched brown."
